Figure X. Median Salary for Males and Females in Post Doc Study by Field. Distribution of median salary for males and females working in positions of post doctoratal study seperated by discipline in 2015. There is no significant difference between male and female median salaries within each field of study [W=19.5, p=0.89] (cliffs delta = 0.04 (negligible)).

Figure X. Median Salary for Males and Females in Post Doc Employment by Field. Distribution of median salary for males and females working in post doctoratal employment seperated by discipline in 2015. There is no significant difference between male and female median salaries within each field of study [W=101, p=0.0026] (cliffs delta = 0.213 (small)).
